<title>mstḥq lạsmk ạltsbyḥ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- (mstḥquⁿ lạsmk ạltsbyḥ .. yạ ạ̹lhnạ wrbnạ ạlmsyḥ)3
 yạ mkẖlṣy ạ̉nt ạldẖbyḥ .. yạ yswʿ ạlmsyḥ
 1- yạ ʿjybaⁿạ yạ msẖyraⁿạ .. yạ ạ̹lhaⁿạ yạ qdyr
 yạ mlykaⁿạ ạ̉bdyaⁿạ .. ạ̉nt rỷys ạlslạm
 hllwyạ sbḥwạ yạh .. hw qdws ʿẓym
 hllwyạ sbḥwạ yạh .. dẖạ mlyk ạlqdysyn
 2- lk ạlmjd qd mlkt .. ạntṣrt yạ qdyr
 qd gẖlbt dst ạlmwt . ạ̉nt qdwsuⁿ ʿẓym
 hllwyạ sbḥwạ yạh .. hw qdws ʿẓym
 hllwyạ sbḥwạ yạh .. dẖạ mlyk ạlqdysyn</lyrics>
</song>